{"tid":976087,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JYP教主 朴軫永因為TWICE新歌收到惡評","createTime":"2019-01-10T06:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T16:17:12.000Z","uid":74065,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c4125c59b0cfd2fc2575e077e9f4ccc948a593b3","tid":976087,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:58:25.000Z","msg":"朴軫永從TWICE粉絲那裏收到惡評。<br />\n上個月12日，TWICE推出特別專輯主打歌The BestThing I Ever Did。<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/VPtJQuZkcXBwP9CEa4p8tWHT9Qo8mSH8fz_C4vTvl_jt-7WoXWdmRvwv75Y23jJL06cDSBEFfRr1BL9UXnSDizRKaR7HHaI58lc=w1600-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FVPtJQuZkcXBwP9CEa4p8tWHT9Qo8mSH8fz_C4vTvl_jt-7WoXWdmRvwv75Y23jJL06cDSBEFfRr1BL9UXnSDizRKaR7HHaI58lc%3Dw1600-rw&h=c7ba6bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">歌曲推出後，粉絲到朴軫永的Instagram上表達不滿。因為這首歌是朴軫永寫的。</span><br />\n<br />\n推出這首歌以後，CEO朴軫永對這首歌做了一些發言「這是我第588首歌，我想要這首歌有好的氣氛，所以我只寫了副歌，完成這段伴奏，然後就交給其他作曲的同事了。他們把歌曲完成，帶來清爽的氣氛。你們怎麼覺得?」<br />\n<br />\n評語充滿批評。TWICE的粉絲毫不隱藏的給他對新歌的回饋。<span style=\"color: red;\">大部分留言都很傷人，比如「不要再給TWICE你的歌」「不要利用TWICE滿足你的貪婪」「我寧可聽到比較好的歌，而不是一直回歸」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ae5767a3c571f759faac914cf789c799e55a96","tid":976087,"uid":138658,"like":34,"dislike":7,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\nd once都係j樣既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d445bcf1f93a67066fae0315eba204a9f1361841","tid":976087,"uid":223790,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:08:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebc2d9d235127b04bdaf5cce204f1fcc6605c0b7","tid":976087,"uid":